    Class Description
    LineRecordReaderFunction
    LineRecordReaderFunction: Used to map a JavaRDD<String> to a JavaRDD<Collection<Writable>> Note that this is most useful with LineRecordReader instances (CSVRecordReader, SVMLightRecordReader, etc)
    RecordReaderFunction
    RecordReaderFunction: Given a RecordReader and a file (via Spark PortableDataStream), load and parse the data into a Collection.
    SequenceRecordReaderFunction
    RecordReaderFunction: Given a SequenceRecordReader and a file (via Spark PortableDataStream), load and parse the sequence data into a Collection>
